<BlogLayout
  title="How Much Music Is AI-Generated? Deezer Says It Just Passed Half"
  description="Over half of daily uploads to Deezer are now fully AI-generated. The numbers behind the flood, and what they mean for producers."
  keywords="how much music is ai generated, ai music statistics, deezer ai music, ai music streaming fraud, fully ai generated music"
  slug="how-much-music-is-ai-generated"
  publishedDate="2026-07-22"
  readTime="5 min read"
